Good morning,

I hope you're doing well. I wanted to reach out and let you know that after more than 8 wonderful years, we have made the difficult decision to close our store in Jamaica, Queens. It's a bittersweet moment for us, as we have enjoyed serving our community and building relationships with our customers.

We want to express our sincere gratitude to all of our loyal customers who have supported us over the years. To show our appreciation, we are offering a special Buy One, Get One Free sale on many items in our Jamaica, Queens store. We hope this sale will allow you to stock up on your favorite products while also saving some money.

Please stop by our Queens store to take advantage of this sale and say goodbye to our team. We would love to see you and express our appreciation for your support over the years.

If there's anything else you need, please don't hesitate to reach out. Thank you again for your support and loyalty.

Best regards,
Mike

166-32 Jamaica Ave,
Jamaica, NY 
718-676-5810

Dear Valued Customers,

It is with mixed emotions that we announce the closure of our store in Jamaica, Queens. Our last day of operation will be Saturday, March 25th. We would like to take this opportunity to express our sincerest gratitude for your unwavering support and loyalty over the years.

We are proud to have been a part of the Jamaica, NY community and to have built relationships with so many of you. As a token of our appreciation, we are offering a special Buy One, Get One Free sale on most items in our store. This is your chance to stock up on your favorite products while saving some money.

We want to remind you that our Brooklyn and Irvington, NJ stores will remain open for your convenience. 

It has been an absolute pleasure serving you, and we will miss being a part of your lives. We hope that you will continue to support other small businesses in the area, as they strive to provide excellent products and services to the community.

Thank you again for your patronage and friendship. We wish you all the best.

Sincerely,

Mike
True Human Hair / Bklyn Hair
166-32 Jamaica Ave, Jamaica, NY
718-291-5810
